The paper discusses the MLPerf benchmark suite, which is a machine learning benchmark suite covering a broad range of applications. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.CV (Computer Vision). The paper also discusses the characteristics of the benchmarks and how they differ from previous benchmarks, which could fall under cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) or cs.AR (Hardware Architecture).
